# A sample conf/backup-src-host file
# ==================================

# Backup a remote host.
remote.example.com

# An alternative sample conf/backup-src-host file
# ===============================================

# Backup a remote host using a different remote user.
backup-user@remote.example.com

# It is also possible to specify the user in conf/backup-src-user and to
# specify only the host in conf/backup-src-host.
